channel.title: New Server Project [Unnamed]
channel.description:
[size=14pt][b]Intro:[/b][/size] Hello mscp, I've been gone from the rsps scene for a while now. I've been mastering VB.NET and C#.NET and I currently started with Unity3D. Though I recently started browsing mscp more and more again, and with no projects in my hands at the moment, I decided to start a new rsps project again.
[size=14pt][b]The project:[/b][/size] My goal is to create a new highly organized and unique base, breaking the meta as they say. I've learned a lot about design and organization while mastering VB and C# and believe I can contribute a decent base to the community. It wont be an apollo or hyperion in terms of stability, but seeing people still hyping on PI I don't think that even matters.
[size=14pt][b]Progress:[/b][/size] [u]Last Update:[/u] 2 February 2014 I just started the project so at this time I have not much yet so I'll just put some media.
[size=14pt][b]Media:[/b][/size]
Package explorer: [img]http://i.imgur.com/Wd4SoAK.png[/img]
Server panel: [img]http://i.imgur.com/gwCtlGG.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/gvNTOcu.png[/img]
For the ones interested, a piece of code that tells you shit. [img]http://i.imgur.com/CGCUawL.png[/img]
